<h1>
  Join the seL4 Foundation!
</h1>
<div>
  <p>
    Become part of the <a title="Membership"
    href="../Membership">members</a> who have already joined the <a
    title="seL4 Foundation" href="../About">seL4 Foundation!</a>.
  </p>
  <p><span class=join>
    Joining is an easy process via the Linux Foundation's <a
    title="Signup page"
    href="https://joinnow.platform.linuxfoundation.org/?project=seL4">online
    signup page</a>.</span>
  </p>
  <p>
    Note that seL4 Foundation members must be (or become) members of the Linux Foundation. The on-line process will include your Linux Foundation membership if you are not already a member.
  </p>
  <p>
  You can review the <a title="Participation Agreement" href="Participation_Agreement_Sample.pdf">seL4 Foundation Fund Participation Agreement</a>.
  </p>
  <p>Questions? Email us at
    <a title="foundation@sel4.systems"
       href=
       "mailto:foundation@sel4.systems">foundation@sel4.systems</a>
  </p>


